6) Distributed Files and Restrictions (implementation-critical)
- Many workflow and agent files are distributed from agentic-lib. Local edits to distributed files will be overwritten by npx @xn-intenton-z2a/agentic-lib init --purge.
- Do not permanently edit distributed files unless you control agentic-lib source. Key distributed locations include .github/workflows/, .github/agentic-lib/, and specific seed files listed in agentic-lib.toml comments.

